More IQA Diatomic "Interaction" Energy Components:
-------------------------------------------------
  Vneen(A,B) = Vne(A,B) + Ven(A,B)
  V_IQA_Inter(A,B) = Vne(A,B) + Ven(A,B) + Vee(A,B) + Vnn(A,B)
                   = VC_IQA_Inter(A,B) + VX_IQA_Inter(A,B)
                   = Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Inter(A,B)
                   = E_IQA_Inter(A,B)
  VC_IQA_Inter(A,B) = Vne(A,B) + Ven(A,B) + VeeC(A,B) + Vnn(A,B)
                    = Coulomb Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Inter(A,B)
                    = E_IQA_Inter(A,B) - VeeX(A,B)
  VX_IQA_Inter(A,B) = VeeX(A,B)
                    = Exchange-Correlation Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Inter(A,B)
                    = E_IQA_Inter(A,B) - VC_IQA_Inter(A,B)
See "2EDM Note" and "DFT Note".
